"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/625905","Ministry of Defence","false","2016-11-08","<p>The Emerging Technology and Innovation Analysis Cell, a Strategic Defence and Security Review 2015 commitment, has since been renamed the Innovation and Research InSight Unit (IRIS) and was launched as part of the Defence Innovation Initiative by the Secretary of State for Defence, in September 2016. IRIS staff are in place and formal funding is due to commence in Financial Year 2017-18. Work is ongoing to determine IRIS's annual budget requirement.</p>","West Worcestershire","Harriett Baldwin",,"2016-11-08T15:51:43.197Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/625905/answer","Biography information for Harriett Baldwin","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/625905/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/625905/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2016-10-31","Ministry of Defence: Innovation","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, what the estimated annual budget is of his Department's Emerging Technology and Innovation Analysis Cell.","false","Biography information for Mr Kevan Jones","North Durham","Mr Kevan Jones","50995"
